    "name": "EVERING",
    "steam_appid": 1876340,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/c54f5c0a7379726be2445cf710dd1a37.avif?t=1727377609\" width=616 height=86 /></span><br><br>《EVERING》是一款像素艺术风格的回合制战斗RPG冒险游戏，在完全独特且细节丰富的循环时间世界中，通过与个性鲜明的角色展开机智诙谐的对话，使史诗故事娓娓道来。<br><br>这是一个和平的时代，世界并未面临危险，但若这个传说被证实为真的……我们的时日恐怕无多。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/986aac20a843aa62c63b4424988bc91f.poster.avif?t=1727377609\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/986aac20a843aa62c63b4424988bc91f.webm?t=1727377609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/986aac20a843aa62c63b4424988bc91f.mp4?t=1727377609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>《EVERING》是一封写给怀旧的情书，致敬我们一起成长的经典游戏，并以焕然一新的面貌呈现出来。游戏没有随机遭遇战，并提供无障碍选项。即使你不想对战，也可以不受惩罚地逃离每场战斗，按照自己的节奏沉浸于故事之中。<br><br>《EVERING》的世界充满了宝藏、大师和水晶，可用以学习全新技能和炼金术原料。更有隐藏秘密藏在你最意料不到的地方。你能全部找到吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/6b1906e41ee6435e6fbfe821145052a9.webp?t=1727377609\" width=616 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>约25小时的游戏时长<br><br></li><li>戏剧性和喜剧性的完美平衡<br><br></li><li>探索多样化的城镇和地下城<br><br></li><li>在回合制战斗中挑战独特的敌人和首领<br><br></li><li>邂逅一群独具特色的角色<br><br></li><li>发现大量构建宏观世界的传说书籍<br><br></li><li>解谜、支线任务等丰富多彩的内容！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/b0a153eae1240dec1435660371464139.poster.avif?t=1727377609\" width=600 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/b0a153eae1240dec1435660371464139.webm?t=1727377609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/b0a153eae1240dec1435660371464139.mp4?t=1727377609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/04c45a014e7841f0d7f90b35e25816bd.webp?t=1727377609\" width=616 height=58 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事剧情</h2><br>欧尼亚王子艾尔达，痴迷于探寻某个传说的起源。为此他倾注毕生心血，常常疏于王室职责。他很快意识到周遭的一切都环环相扣，这将引领他发现一些从未设想过的真相。<br><br>与他同行的将有芦，一位强大且充满保护欲的女巫；乔夫拉，一位擅长刀技的神秘浪人；拉里克，一位潜力无限却自卑怯懦的炼金术学徒；还有绮拜恩，一位孜孜以求灵感的艺术家。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >跟随传奇英雄的脚步，书写属于你自己的不朽传奇。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876340/extras/c22e919ceea3fd0194df98375a0b312e.avif?t=1727377609\" width=616 height=347 /></span>",
